JSE-listed Impala Platinum Holdings (Implats) has concluded agreements to acquire a further one-million shares in Royal Bafokeng Platinum (RBPlat), taking its shareholding in the company to 45.66%. Implats is progressing an acquisition of all the issued share capital of RBPlat, at an offer of R90 a share and 0.3 of an Implats share for every RBPlat share held.